# Wizard Wars — Project Context

Multiplayer top-down (35° angle) arena shooter. 2–12 players per match, WASD movement, abilities, shop, lives (starting lives from balance config).

## Architecture
- **Runtime**: Bun 1.2 (see `package.json` `packageManager`)
- **Web**: Next.js 16 App Router
- **API**: tRPC v11 + SuperJSON
- **HTTP**: Express 5 (`server.ts` co-hosts Next + Colyseus)
- **WebSockets**: Colyseus 0.17 rooms (`chat`, `game_lobby`)
- **Game Client**: Phaser 4 (Arena scene — Phaser Editor compatible); default canvas **1344×768** (`src/game/config.ts`)
- **Game Server**: bitECS 0.4 server-authoritative simulation at **60 Hz** (`TICK_RATE_HZ`, `TICK_MS` in `src/shared/balance-config/rendering.ts`; loop in `GameLobbyRoom`)
- **Database**: PostgreSQL 16 + Prisma 6
- **Auth**: jose JWT + bcryptjs, cookie name `ww-token`

## Key constants
- **World / sim bounds**: 66×53 tiles × 64px = **4224×3392** px (`ARENA_LAYOUT_*` in `src/shared/balance-config/arena-layout.ts`); center **(2112, 1696)** (`ARENA_CENTER_*` in `arena.ts`)
- **Spawns**: **12** committed safe points (`ARENA_LAYOUT_SPAWN_POINTS`); not a fixed-radius ring (`ARENA_SPAWN_RING_RADIUS_PX` is legacy/approximate only)
- Max players: 12 (`MAX_PLAYERS_PER_MATCH` in `src/shared/balance-config/lobby.ts`)
- Player: `PLAYER_RADIUS_PX` 20; world collision ellipse 20×9 px (`combat.ts`); base move speed **200** px/s (`BASE_MOVE_SPEED_PX_PER_SEC`)

